trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of related sections within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção das seções relacionadas dentro de um arquivo de configuração.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionCollection> class to iterate through a collection of <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> objects.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionCollection> classe para iterar por meio de uma coleção de <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> objetos.

trans-unit.source: You can access this collection of objects using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Sections%2A> property or the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionGroup.Sections%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Você pode acessar essa coleção de objetos usando o <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Sections%2A> propriedade ou o <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionGroup.Sections%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionCollection> class is also used in the creation of custom types that extend the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionCollection> classe também é usada na criação de tipos personalizados que estendem o <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> classe.
